  <chunk id="1054ed358dfede6e22877513169bef30c491c363.c3" text="Conclusions/Significance: This study demonstrates that CIITA enhances HIV Gag processing, and provides the first evidence of a novel, post-transcriptional, cytoplasmic function for a well-known transactivator."/>
